/4356IBUF\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002677\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002677\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Agostiniani\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2009\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>115-116, no.1 fig. 2\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/63R3F4J2\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002427\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002427\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mignosa\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2017-2018\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>217, no. 3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EBZBFTF\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002428\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002428\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
